    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Consists largely of glauconite, a greenish granular mineral containing up to 25% iron, with a large percentage of silica and some potash and aluminum, used especially as a water softener and as a source of potash.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
